---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import TrustedBy from '../components/TrustedBy.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="Catering Richmond BC | Indian Catering for Weddings & Corporate Events"
	description="Indian catering Richmond BC for weddings, corporate offices, YVR-area events, and private parties. Halal, vegan, vegetarian. Award-winning since 2010."
	canonical="/catering-richmond"
	ogImage="https://sulacatering.com/uploads/wedding-food-catering-vancouver-bc.webp"
>

	<Fragment slot="schema">
		<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
			"@context": "https://schema.org","@type": "Service",
			"name": "Catering Richmond",
			"provider": {"@id": "https://sulacatering.com/#organization"},
			"areaServed": {"@type": "City", "name": "Richmond"},
			"serviceType": "Indian Catering"
		})} />
	</Fragment>

	<section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(20,8,16,0.85) 0%, rgba(38,14,38,0.7) 50%, rgba(20,8,16,0.9) 100%), url('/uploads/catering-near-me-vancouver-food-parties.webp');">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<h1>Catering<br/>in <em>Richmond</em></h1>
			<p class="hero-tagline">Indian catering across Richmond, Steveston to Bridgeport, YVR-area corporate events, and home weddings.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Request Richmond Catering</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TrustedBy />


	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="intro-block reveal">
				<h2>Indian Catering for <em>Richmond Events</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
				<p>Richmond's food standards are no joke. The city eats out on a level most other suburbs don't, and the families we cater for know what's authentic and what's softened for an audience. We don't soften. Our halal sourcing is rigorous, our vegetarian and Jain prep happens in dedicated areas, and the spice levels are dialled to the rooms we're feeding. Whether it's a Steveston home wedding, a Brighouse Diwali, or a year-end <a href="/corporate" class="body-link">corporate catering</a> lunch out near YVR, the food shows up the way you'd want it.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<img src="/uploads/wedding-food-catering-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Indian wedding food catering Richmond BC" class="full-width-image" loading="lazy" />

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">What We Cater in Richmond</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Every <em>Richmond Event</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="service-grid-v2">
				<a href="/weddings" class="service-card-v2 reveal">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/wedding-catering-services.webp" alt="Wedding catering Richmond" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Richmond Weddings</span>
							<h3>Wedding <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Multi-cultural and South Asian weddings across Richmond banquet halls and home venues.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Weddings →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/corporate" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-100">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/catering-service-vancouver-office.webp" alt="Corporate catering Richmond" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">YVR Corridor · Bridgeport</span>
							<h3>Corporate <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Office lunches and conference catering for Richmond's corporate parks and YVR-adjacent businesses.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Corporate →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/private-parties" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-200">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/Indian-food-catering-private-party.webp" alt="Private party Richmond" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Steveston · Brighouse</span>
							<h3>Private <em>Parties</em></h3>
							<p>Birthdays, Diwali, anniversaries, at homes and venues across every Richmond neighbourhood.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Private →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
				<a href="/cafe-catering" class="service-card-v2 reveal delay-300">
					<div class="service-card-img">
						<img src="/uploads/indian-food-catering-near-me-vancouver-bc.webp" alt="Cafe catering Richmond" loading="lazy" />
						<div class="service-card-overlay">
							<span class="service-eyebrow">Chai · Coffee · Pastries</span>
							<h3>Café <em>Catering</em></h3>
							<p>Live masala chai bars and barista coffee service for Richmond weddings and corporate events.</p>
							<span class="service-arrow">Explore Café →</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-plum pattern-mandala">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="experience">
				<div class="experience-img reveal-left">
					<img src="/uploads/best-catering-vancouver.webp" alt="Authentic Indian catering Richmond" loading="lazy" />
				</div>
				<div class="experience-content reveal-right">
					<h2>We Know <em>Richmond</em></h2>
					<p>A lot of our Richmond bookings come with one easy ask: stay close to home cooking. So we don't reinvent. We cook the regional dishes the way they're cooked, draw on the kitchen knowledge we've built over fifteen years, and let the food do the talking.</p>
					<p>Delivery from our Vancouver kitchens runs about 25 minutes off-peak. We also cater across <a href="/catering-vancouver" class="body-link">Vancouver</a>, <a href="/catering-burnaby" class="body-link">Burnaby</a>, and <a href="/catering-surrey" class="body-link">Surrey</a>.</p>
					<div class="experience-stats">
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">25min</div><div class="stat-label">Delivery</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">$5</div><div class="stat-label">Flat Fee</div></div>
						<div class="stat-item"><div class="stat-number">15+</div><div class="stat-label">Years</div></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section section-cream">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="text-center reveal">
				<p class="eyebrow">Common Questions</p>
				<h2 class="mag-title">Richmond Catering <em>FAQs</em></h2>
				<div class="gold-divider-ornament"><span></span><div class="diamond"></div><span></span></div>
			</div>
			<div class="faq-list">
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you cater Richmond banquet halls?</h3><p>Yes, most major Richmond banquet halls allow outside catering. We handle setup, service, and breakdown.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>How fast is delivery to Richmond?</h3><p>Our Vancouver kitchens deliver to Richmond within 25 minutes off-peak. Temperature-controlled transport.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Do you offer halal Indian catering for Richmond events?</h3><p>Yes, all our chicken and lamb is halal-certified, sourced from trusted local BC suppliers.</p></div>
				<div class="faq-item reveal"><h3>Can you cater near YVR?</h3><p>Yes, we frequently cater corporate events near the airport and Bridgeport-area businesses.</p></div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>


	<section class="cta-section">
		<div class="reveal">
			<h2>Catering for <em>Richmond</em></h2>
			<p>Tell us your venue, your headcount, your timeline.</p>
			<a href="https://sulaindianrestaurant.com/sula-catering-order/" class="btn btn-gold">Request a Quote</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>
